## ததஅக

[ iṉām ]  
  
பெ. u. inām  
1. gift froma superior to an inferior  
present  
reward; நன்கொடை  
2. grant of land made by government for religious or charitable purposes or forservices rendered  
sometimes given rentfreeand sometimes with a light quitrent; மானியம்  
s. (hind.) present  
gift  
bonus  
reward  
வெகுமதி;  
